  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3313_11",
    "text": "1.研究人员进行了多种植物激素对豌豆植 株侧芽生长影响的实验，结果如图所示。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11182294700058241,
      0.6033333333333334,
      0.48456610366919045,
      0.6383333333333333
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3313",
    "order": 19
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3313_12",
    "text": "a去顶芽，切口涂抹赤霉素 100 ,b去顶芽 80 c顶芽保留，侧芽上涂抹细胞 60 分裂素 80 d去顶芽，切口涂抹生长素 1 c顶芽保留 2 4 6 8 10 12",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
